{
  "info": {
    "name": "Smart City Platform - Kelompok 4 (Server)",
    "_postman_id": "smart-city-kelompok4-server",
    "description": "Koleksi API Smart City Platform - Deployed di Server\n\nBase URL: http://103.147.92.135\n\nService yang tersedia:\n- API Gateway (Port 3040) - Kelompok 4\n- Auth Service (Port 3042) - Kelompok 4\n- Environment Service (Port 8042) - Kelompok 4\n- Traffic Service (Port 8041) - Kelompok 4\n- Citizen Service (Port 8040) - Kelompok 4\n- ML Service (Port 5040) - Kelompok 4\n\nCara penggunaan:\n1. Register user terlebih dahulu (1.1 atau 1.2)\n2. Login untuk mendapatkan token (1.3 atau 1.4)\n3. Set token ke variable environment 'token'\n4. Testing endpoints dengan Bearer token\n\nGrant Types:\n- password: Login user (citizen/operator)\n- refresh_token: Perpanjang token expired\n- client_credentials: IoT / Service-to-Service",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
